{"tid":1098751,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"怎樣簡易地同兔子剪指甲? (補充!)","createTime":"2019-04-09T09:42:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-17T11:49:02.000Z","uid":197098,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"185ef0aa8e12597447f61a5bc4308fcf7a770e1d","tid":1098751,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T09:42:26.000Z","msg":"這個方法剪指甲先至最容易(美國兔子協會提供的video)，因為這個方法對兔子來說反而比較少壓力(stress), 越少壓力越容易，反而越多人越大壓力：<br />\n<br />\n<strong>把兔子放在桌上剪，桌上放條毛巾給他站著因為有traction。</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/W9KemnaTGIs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FW9KemnaTGIs&d=Srnh2QCYUB68P60bIi3tLbc9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=555b828a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/W9KemnaTGIs</a> <br />\n<br />\n記住不要反轉隻兔仔放喺你大髀上好似bb咁，咁樣會令到佢進入昏睡狀態，心臟跳動越來越慢，有啲兔仔因為咁而死咗，以下video 有解釋：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/rvausPZOJ5A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FrvausPZOJ5A&d=Srnh2QCYUB68P60bIi3tLbc9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=943fc2d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/rvausPZOJ5A</a> <br />\n<br />\n我見過有寵物店反轉佢好似BB咁來剪指甲，所以原來好多人都唔知。"},{"pid":"2ce53a08b78e8a4066a54d0ebb567c65d6449e1d","tid":1098751,"uid":41914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T09:55:06.000Z","msg":"天竺鼠岩用呢招嗎..."},{"pid":"abe18be7476e2b76d28bd77bd8e46683ab9f076d","tid":1098751,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2ce53a08b78e8a4066a54d0ebb567c65d6449e1d","tid":1098751,"uid":41914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T09:55:06.000Z","msg":"天竺鼠岩用呢招嗎..."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T13:15:22.000Z","msg":"你有養天竺鼠？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"730b137d4bc743d73d10987d4bd27b8a9fca9ba2","tid":1098751,"uid":41914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"abe18be7476e2b76d28bd77bd8e46683ab9f076d","tid":1098751,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid"