e Rabbit Society), 他們說這個動作是不建議的，另外他們說有些診所用兩個人同兔子剪指甲反而令到牠有壓力，越少人就越少壓力，這個方法是對兔子來說是最少壓力，他們說有些兔子在過程中瞓咗覺。<br />\n<br />\n以下video 是The Dodo提供的，The Dodo 是一個有權威性的國際愛護動物組織, 他們在video 內有解釋為什麼不要這樣做：因為他們會進入Trance, 對於兔子來說是terrifying(非常驚慌)<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/O3s6UiCIS3I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FO3s6UiCIS3I&d=Srnh2QCYUB68P60bIi3tLbc9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=b86717d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/O3s6UiCIS3I</a><br />\n<br />\n以下video(0:55-1:53)是101Rabbits提供(在美國Rabbit community𥚃很有名的YouTuber, 專提供Original resources)，有<strong><ins>詳盡</ins></strong>解釋<strong><ins>兩種原因</ins></strong>點解唔好咁做, 請自己聽聽解釋：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Ek7YkW2T4Zk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FEk7YkW2T4Zk&d=Srnh2QCYUB68P60bIi3tLbc9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=390f468e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Ek7YkW2T4Zk</a><br />\n<br />\n我都係在House Rabbit Society US和 <a href=\"http://rabbitspeak.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frabbitspeak.com&d=Srnh2QCYUB68P60bIi3tLbc9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=7244a7bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">rabbitspeak.com</a> 等引用出來。我自己都係用這個方法去同兔剪指甲，放在桌上剪，放條毛巾給他站着因為有traction，事實上比較容易去剪。"},{"pid":"6d85407bdd1f2792641961ca5515c828a9ca31eb","tid":1098751,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"978b00dfc253ec3d1ca87b7d3b94c3ac0228ea58","tid":1098751,"uid":121831,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T15:45:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/w6FAumVBLr8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fw6FAumVBLr8&d=Srnh2QCYUB68P60bIi3tLbc9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=68b7053f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/w6FAumVBLr8</a><br />\n但我睇好多寵物美容師都會反轉佢黎剪<br />\n如果俾佢四腳踏地，佢唔會剪剪吓跑走咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T03:48:57.000Z","msg":"地下剪就會逃走，桌上剪就唔會，另外要放毛巾在桌上給他站着，因為有traction"},{"pid":"e3113ceb5ed59a0b4d674c983ad96cedf208b269","tid":1098751,"uid":197098,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T02:26:00.000Z","msg":"我問了House Rabbit Society (美國兔子協會)為什麼反轉兔子放在大腿上剪指甲是危險⚠️，原來會令到兔子有很大壓力，可引致心臟病。他們的回應：<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Some people put the rabbit in a towel to subdue them- but be careful because it can stress them out. Flipping them on their back can be dangerous because it&lsquo;s stressful and can give them a heart attack. Can you find someone else to hold the rabbit while you trim the nails? Alternatively, can you find a vet who will help and show you how?&rdquo;"},{"pid":"7169898bda917af5d7b18005ce2320ed3539e27c","tid":1098751,"uid":197098,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T11:49:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>兔子的食物和份量- 注意! </ins></strong>🐰🌟</span><br />\n<br />\n根據美國兔子協會(House Rabbit Society):<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">每天怎樣餵BB和青少年(7星期-7個月大):</span><br />\n- 24小時無限乾草: 1/3 Alfalfa Hay, 2/3 Timothy Hay, 可以加Orchard Hay, Oat Hay 或其他Hay令到更多元化和好味道，任你喜歡:loveliness:<br />\n- 2湯匙-無限兔糧：推介Burgess或Oxbow幼兔糧，其他牌子也可以<br />\n- 12個星期大或以上: 開始給吃1-3條手指長的蔬菜 (要徹底清洗)<br />\n<br />\n<em>注意：</em>24小時無限兔糧是沒問題，但如果牠只吃糧不吃乾草就要減少兔糧，因為消化系統還在生長中，乾草是最重要。喝煲過的冷水，不要給自來水和礦泉水。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">怎樣餵年輕成人(7個月-1歲)：</span><br />\n- 24小時無限乾草: 減少Alfalfa Hay, 增加Timothy Hay和其他Hay<br />\n- 減少到每6磅(兔子體重)半杯兔糧<br />\n- 漸漸地增加蔬菜<br />\n<br />\n- 極少水果: 每6磅(兔子體重)1-2安士<br />\n<br />\n<em>注意：</em>如果兔子有5磅，未夠6磅，可以盛載半杯兔糧後再倒走1/3或1/4糧，自己調校<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">餵成熟成人(1-5歲)：</span><br />\n- 24小時無限乾草：移除Alfalfa Hay, 只供Timothy Hay, Orchard Hay, Oat Hay等等<br />\n- 每6磅1/4-1/2杯糧<br />\n- 每6磅最少2杯切好的蔬菜<br />\n/每2磅1杯切好的蔬菜<br />\n<br />\n- 每6磅2安士或以下(2湯匙)水果/每2磅1茶匙(teaspoon)水果<br />\n<br />\n<em>注意：</em>如果兔子有5磅，未夠6磅，可以盛載半杯兔糧後再倒走1/3或1/4糧，自己調校<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">老兔(6歲以上)：</span><br />\n- 如果兔子能夠維持足夠體重，可以繼續供給以上的食法<br />\n- 年老和身體虛弱的需要增加兔糧，體重過輕的可以給吃Alfalfa Hay(前提是體內鈣質正常)。老兔最好定期去驗血。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">如果我餵很少糧或不餵糧，怎樣補充營養？</span><br />\n- 需要增加蔬菜份量來補充營養，(而卡路里是不需要補充的)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<em>更多資訊：</em><a href=\"https://rabbit.org/faq-diet/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Frabbit.org%2Ffaq-diet%2F&d=Srnh2QCYUB68P60bIi3tLbc9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=dca14837\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://rabbit.org/faq-diet/</a><br />\n                <a href=\"https://rabbit.org/suggested-vegetables-and-fruits-for-a-rabbit-diet/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Frabbit.org%2Fsuggested-vegetables-and-fruits-for-a-rabbit-diet%2F&d=Srnh2QCYUB68P60bIi3tLbc9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=008e60dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://rabbit.org/suggested-vegetables-and-fruits-for-a-rabbit-diet/</a>"}]}